Class MatrixMultiplication

java.lang.Object
  ru.ifmo.ctddev.kovanikov.task6.MatrixMultiplication

public class MatrixMultiplication
extends java.lang.Object

The MatrixMultiplication class realizes matrix multiplication in several threads.

Gets matrix size n and number of threads m from command-line arguments, creates two matrices with size n * n, multiplies them using Math.min(n * n, m) threads, sets result into third matrix and writes elapsed time and sum of resulting matrix into standard output.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Dmitriy Kovanikov
